																"TagText": {
																	"handle": "hae8f363bge1e8g41e1g9f37g68984bafd030",
																	"value": "But Lae'zel said it anyway, to her immense credit. She's choosing truth, she's choosing freedom - for her, for Orpheus, for the githyanki people.",
